# MetalFusion website — environment variables
# Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local`) and fill the values.
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY: Every variable prefixed with VITE_ is BAKED INTO THE PUBLIC
# BROWSER BUNDLE at build time. It is readable by anyone who visits the site.
# Only put PUBLIC site keys here (Web3Forms public key, GA4 measurement ID,
# GSC verification token). NEVER put server secrets, API tokens, database
# passwords, or anything that gives write access to a third-party account.

# --- Contact form ---
# Web3Forms access key (free, EU-compatible static-site form provider).
# Get one at https://web3forms.com — paste the key here.
# Without it, the form will fall back to showing the info@metalfusion.hu mailto link.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=

# --- Spam protection (optional) ---
# Cloudflare Turnstile site key (https://www.cloudflare.com/products/turnstile/).
# Leave empty to use only honeypot + time-gate protection.
VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=

# --- Analytics (consent-gated) ---
# Google Analytics 4 Measurement ID, e.g. G-XXXXXXXXXX.
# When set, gtag is loaded AFTER the visitor accepts analytics cookies.
VITE_GA4_ID=

# --- Search Console verification ---
# The value of the `content` attribute from Google Search Console's HTML meta tag method.
# E.g. for <meta name="google-site-verification" content="abc123..."> set:
# VITE_GSC_VERIFICATION=abc123...
VITE_GSC_VERIFICATION=

# --- Live domain (optional override) ---
# If the live site lives on a different domain than the default metalfusion.hu,
# set the full origin here (no trailing slash). Used by canonical URLs, OG and sitemap.
VITE_SITE_BASE_URL=
